body:
What the PR does
- The new release v2.3.0.1 has been added.
- The checksum of v2.2.1.1 changed due to the issue discussed here https://github.com/precice/python-bindings/issues/109. Upstream is informed and works on a solution. If everything works out fine, the checksums of v2.3.0.1 and newer version will not change anymore.
title: [py-pyprecice] add v2.3.0.1 and fix hash of v2.2.1.1
